## Context
This is a Spring Boot 3.4.5 + Java 21 project. We're adding document tagging to the SpaceNode system. Follow existing patterns exactly (Star feature is the reference).

Key patterns:
- Entity: extends BaseEntity, @TableName(keepGlobalPrefix = true, value = "xxx"), @SuperBuilder
- BaseEntity provides: id (ASSIGN_ID snowflake), isDeleted (@TableLogic), createdBy, updatedBy, createdAt, updatedAt
- Mapper: extends BaseMapper
- Service interface: IXxxService extends IService
- Service impl: IXxxServiceImpl extends ServiceImpl (note: I prefix kept on impl class name)
- RO: @Data, @Schema, validation annotations
- BasePageRo has pageNum (default 1) and pageSize (default 25)
- created_by/updated_by columns are varchar(255) type in DB

